Class Rate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lightningj.paywall.JSONParsable
      • org.lightningj.paywall.btcpayserver.vo.Rate

  • public class Rate
extends JSONParsable
    Value object representing one BTC Pay Server JSON rate. Doesn't implement the full API just the necessary parts to integrate with paywall-core requirements. Created by philip on 2018-10-17.
